          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "However, there are some challenges ahead of them. I suspect that some people in the influencer marketing world are ill-disposed to add more transparency to the process. An industry that doesn't pay to much attention to outcomes is an easier one for both agencies and influencers — although clearly ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "that is beginning to change",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://variety.com/2018/biz/news/luka-sabbat-snap-spectacles-1203015434/",
            "version": 1
